  "logNo": "222945917418",
  "title": "[스티커] 초소형 도무송스티커 Ⅰ",
  "addDate": "2022. 12. 6.",
  "categoryNo": "47",
  "url": "https://m.blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/222945917418",
  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-843dbe6b-c7e4-44b4-9b21-2728158c606a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-6cac98c6-308c-4b71-80b2-901025efa460\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c49abb9f-8607-4aad-a489-cecb8d2a134e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">스티커는 어떤 상품에 접착하여 붙이는 용도로 사용됩니다. 제품 설명서등에 활용되기도 하고 홍보용으로 자신의 제품에 붙여 광고로 활용되기도 합니다. 요즘은 굿즈나 인스용 스티커로 판매목적의 상품이 많이 출시되고 있습니다. 자신의 디자인 캐릭터가 상품으로 자신이 있으신 분은 언제든지 연락주십시요.~ 그런 인스제품은 투명스티커나 아트지 스티커를 많이 활용합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-4d3ec1dc-dbeb-44db-a42a-8e2bcfe4ca12\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-0e7144f9-bff3-4abb-93c2-91a70b1bb707\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-64b53764-0e81-400b-ab9e-9842a079c8c0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-f8dba09e-48c3-43c8-9fa6-470a7b694202\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMDFfMjA0/MDAxNjY5ODcxNjcxNTc0.3MvYyZZ01DOhgLzZcGe4NvXBkqxLYLxBSD8pvd21iPUg.iJTfYr66cbG3a-VPHSHGdcfbpuWrap5O-dA__KcCeSQg.PNG.cookthedesign/30_%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85_221112.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"828\", \"originalHeight\" : \"238\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMDFfMjA0/MDAxNjY5ODcxNjcxNTc0.3MvYyZZ01DOhgLzZcGe4NvXBkqxLYLxBSD8pvd21iPUg.iJTfYr66cbG3a-VPHSHGdcfbpuWrap5O-dA__KcCeSQg.PNG.cookthedesign/30_%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85_221112.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-89660805-caa8-45e7-8f54-dfc65f87e7ae\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5a40fdb2-9cf3-4178-aa4c-594cf8cade2c\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>기본 종이, 아트지 백색 90g, 투명지 38g</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e49bafc2-9343-4f40-9a95-f4323ca2fa18\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3e3cd8f8-72fe-45bd-8636-d221e1a9998e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">스티커의 종이는 기본적으로 접착력에 따라 구분이 됩니다. 접착은 강한 접착력이 있는 것과 붙였다가 띌 수 있는 접착력을 가지고 있는 3M계열, 또는 띌때 자국이 남지 않는 리무벌스티커등으로 구별이 됩니다. 일반적으로는 한번 붙이면 떨어지지 않는 강접스티커를 사용합니다. 또는 후지라고 말하는 후면종이는 거의 대부분 노란색이지만 특별히 백색이나 다른색으로 생산되기도 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7fc6832b-6a53-4853-9189-7d57f17d1cc0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f955b732-12d9-4ced-a654-3a7c396f7f31\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4955a5d8-31cc-4e06-bf59-46283211fef9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ea128e54-ad55-4560-a1c7-accb93293098\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">기본 종이로는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-df22e1d3-29ad-47c5-851e-2ea05570c613\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-66c1b55b-14df-4e6a-9f38-9e89c7ab2011\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">아트지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4d568f33-5c09-4447-940a-cfee6a2f6992\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-37ef171b-9552-4416-9174-194753c0c6bb\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-42ccf868-5108-481b-a0a1-56e00fbb61ac\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">유포지 무광PP</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-44114cfc-754b-44a8-8651-475c1587c5e2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2d8ea0af-504c-4295-be5c-915510f1ca01\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">은무데드롱 무광</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a2f7894f-0878-44be-879a-77f8c8c057d3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-306ba75a-0f8d-4cf0-9291-6fa720694f49\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">투명데드롱 유광</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3f89ded4-6f13-49ab-b639-f0083776d9e5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3b42b216-77d9-4352-ace5-a977ff96e957\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">크라프트</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-96d35e74-2cfd-4a5c-a6ec-644baa105a49\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-36e3818f-1c00-4003-b944-9eca02dd91ff\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">리무벌</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8db5585e-cdfc-4bf8-96e1-9a4524276ee7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6974e7f2-2140-4360-8858-ccc85b05c633\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">PVC</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b5f7e3ab-73ef-45be-b9a1-8c5c6d9d8f2b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6ba14a6d-c455-407c-9ee2-ec6b112d1969\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">로 구분됩니다. 더 다양한 종이는 선택 가능합니다. 다만 종이를 별도로 사용하시면 단가나 납기가 달라질 수 있습니다. 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-150d1545-bc81-4ce4-b6ba-68e9c2b53786\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d6ca3c25-20f3-4412-b27a-92ee9e9f1949\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-d6ca3c25-20f3-4412-b27a-92ee9e9f1949\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMDRfNTEg/MDAxNjcwMTQ4NTM4NDMw.nafG31GRxe4f6CwzmUWQzkC9Da-KQcxn3xGkxlLxg4Ig.dC9FoGKXlyROxcwP71wIetIR_ssrZg9vtqK0k5syIKEg.JPEG.cookthedesign/KakaoTalk_20221204_190801402_03.jp