ection se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-9e4fbf4a-4cb3-4b6b-ba86-ed00136cfa17\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMDRfMTQg/MDAxNjcwMTUwNjg4MTUz.8pNJcXn6EMOdLv_XZZezkcKiVVFAcNh8gC8utpFWKxsg.MMtR0ejsS0s7vQR260TomJEH7xIkFR2xZNuqXmXtBOcg.PNG.cookthedesign/02_%EC%82%AC%EA%B0%81%EB%AA%85%ED%95%A8_%ED%85%9C%ED%94%8C%EB%A6%BF.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1477\", \"originalHeight\" : \"769\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMDRfMTQg/MDAxNjcwMTUwNjg4MTUz.8pNJcXn6EMOdLv_XZZezkcKiVVFAcNh8gC8utpFWKxsg.MMtR0ejsS0s7vQR260TomJEH7xIkFR2xZNuqXmXtBOcg.PNG.cookthedesign/02_%EC%82%AC%EA%B0%81%EB%AA%85%ED%95%A8_%ED%85%9C%ED%94%8C%EB%A6%BF.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6a232f95-49a7-4568-81a1-7f223369f244\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-519c1911-ec2b-4b8c-8cf8-5805fc56d159\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c86160c6-e698-4235-a096-b02bd1c5c8fc\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">이 부분은 제작사에서 결정할 사항입니다. 다만 기본적인 사이즈가 어디까지 되는지 문의가 많아서 적어드려 봅니다. 최소사이즈에 대한 문의는 (주)파파스컴퍼니에 문의주시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f233ca56-4fa5-442d-965e-c9e13fa9d901\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F222945917418#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-f68b5cd5-2b16-4a12-81e8-de9430f60682\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-400508e6-75c3-4f25-a0fe-4d8758154a59\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMDFfMjI4/MDAxNjY5ODcwNjQ3MDI3._X3DsScv80AcA7G6_lj_-RxmK3CP8CaMBIcPD2sSTpcg.PjDaXZ95tKSsVciIdzrsN64gR7bPcu8WcdlK9qTSUc0g.PNG.cookthedesign/30_%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85_221112.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"828\", \"originalHeight\" : \"237\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMDFfMjI4/MDAxNjY5ODcwNjQ3MDI3._X3DsScv80AcA7G6_lj_-RxmK3CP8CaMBIcPD2sSTpcg.PjDaXZ95tKSsVciIdzrsN64gR7bPcu8WcdlK9qTSUc0g.PNG.cookthedesign/30_%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85_221112.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-11d77860-2cca-4b04-974d-b98a308fba6c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a90bfbfb-59b0-4a01-9086-8f6eb72592e3\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>소형사이즈 스티커는 이렇게 주문하세요.</b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8eb9c0ba-769e-40ae-b809-df7a3e6aedb6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b5f9600f-4e26-460f-a3df-f478127b2158\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">사이즈가 작은 스티커는 재단으로 작업이 불가능합니다. 작업도 까다롭고 포장이나 구분이 되야하는 제품이라면 더더욱 사이즈에 대한 고려가 필요합니다. 다음 사항을 고려하여 주문하세요.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b5c9b15a-c850-4753-bb1c-355c7786ca39\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7050af09-5494-4ce6-aaf1-612388661fd9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-093cc760-282e-4ebd-a4ed-7ffb2d1c0486\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-99b8e56e-7995-4d18-80a1-8d78a43abf12\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">어떤 용도로 사용될 것인가? 사이즈를 붙이는 용도를 정해 주문을 하셔야 합니다. 종이와 접착력을 고려한 사양을 결정하시기 바랍니다. 제품에 붙이는 용도나 홍보용이라는 용도는 구별하여 종이를 선택해 주시기 바랍니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-044c0de5-d015-47bf-8a37-d7cee78fc5c1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-dc31adc9-3d8a-491a-a67b-c68a76378752\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">종이와 접착력이 결정되었다면 제품에 붙이는 사이즈를 정해야 합니다. 사이즈가 일반적인 것이라면 비용이나 납기가 대단히 저렴해 질 수 있습니다. 하지만 사이즈가 오늘의 예시처럼 초소형이거나 초대형이라면.... 또는 모양을 따는 것이라면 비용과 납기를 고려해 주시기 바랍니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-086e09e0-314c-4a80-a38d-c6a9884e6454\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ea8f1861-2425-4b8f-b988-2fc1888f1357\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">종이, 접착력, 사이즈가 정해 졌다면 디자인을 위한 준비를 하십시요. 그리고 수량이나 디자인에 따라 단가나 납기가 완전히 달라질 수 있으니 반드시 수량과 납기를 확인해 주시기 바랍니다.</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ed9ae631-348a-483d-8c19-e6111f1962ab\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b75e2808-021b-4892-aff9-24510b16a218\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e1a54d7b-06fc-4c7c-8c2c-5612aea295ac\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-e1a54d7b-06fc-4c7c-8c2c-5612aea295ac\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMDRfMTk2/MDAxNjcwMTUyOTk1NTQ4.CbJW3Yed7yRBSLK8tPyFg26jFz4QMPV2ZwevpkhPEXUg.KB4hi2D2Ce5k7NvaZf4EaKjBHDmAHgrAzAJU0XCe09Mg.JPEG.cookthedesign/KakaoTalk_20221204_202221645.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1440\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1080\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMDRfMTk2/MDAxNjcwMTUyOTk1NTQ4.CbJW3Yed7yRBSLK8tPyFg26jFz4QMPV2ZwevpkhPEXUg.KB4hi2D2Ce5k7NvaZf4EaKjBHDmAHgrAzAJU0XCe09Mg.JPEG.cookthedesign/KakaoTalk_20221204_202221645.jpg?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-99c8fa7b-afc4-43aa-b414-aa519694fc72\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:736px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-99c8fa7b-afc4-43aa-b414-aa519694fc72\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMDRfOTcg/MDAxNjcwMTUxMzI3NjA1.hGRarbgGaYLdbOwkoBvCt6z-GWmCzJueHmBKweAsXIAg.R2_V7jekCRhGDTfBbkiMw0ODkH-IZJmieWh674E38AQg.PNG.cookthedesign/%EC%9B%90%EC%B0%BD%ED%9B%88_%EB%B0%B0%EB%84%88.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"736\", \"originalHeight\" : \"130\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMDRfOTcg/MDAxNjcwMTUxMzI3NjA1.hGRarbgGaYLdbOwkoBvCt6z-GWmCzJueHmBKweAsXIAg.R2_V7jekCRhGDTfBbkiMw0ODkH-IZJmieWh674E38AQg.PNG.cookthedesign/%EC%9B%90%EC%B0%BD%ED%9B%88_%EB%B0%B0%EB%84%88.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a6719f84-6141-414f-87e8-8127951ef2e8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f4e7e9a8-2175-4d17-99e5-31163c297c47\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f17dbb12-eaa3-4f46-afb7-5a244b776963\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
